2
00:00:00.310 --> 00:00:03.180
Open up the borderless map, then

3
00:00:03.180 --> 00:00:06.380
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

4
00:00:06.380 --> 00:00:10.770
LET’S SAIL ON right now, hoist your sails up high

5
00:00:10.770 --> 00:00:13.760
Riding on the wind

6
00:00:18.890 --> 00:00:23.100
DON’T GIVE UP, it’s time to finish what we started

7
00:00:23.290 --> 00:00:26.070
So don't you grow disheartened

8
00:00:26.380 --> 00:00:29.830
Laugh the tears away through the storm

9
00:00:30.030 --> 00:00:34.260
SHOUT IT OUT, when you feel down always remember

10
00:00:34.600 --> 00:00:36.860
That’s what your friends are there for

11
00:00:36.890 --> 00:00:39.020
Y’know there’s no point in fronting,

12
00:00:39.020 --> 00:00:42.940
your crew will always have your back

13
00:00:43.310 --> 00:00:47.040
Even in the face of utter darkness

14
00:00:47.270 --> 00:00:50.030
C’mon, BRAVE IT OUT We’ll be alright

15
00:00:50.330 --> 00:00:53.820
Together you know that we’ll never lose a fight

16
00:00:54.040 --> 00:00:56.810
Open up the borderless map, then

17
00:00:56.830 --> 00:00:59.670
Head for that unknown edge of the ocean

18
00:00:59.970 --> 00:01:04.250
All great journeys starts with a single step

19
00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:05.260
DREAMIN’ ON

20
00:01:05.260 --> 00:01:08.040
Open up the borderless map, then

21
00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:10.780
Raise the flag we swore to defend

22
00:01:10.930 --> 00:01:13.670
We’ll never stop until we’ve reached the top

23
00:01:13.740 --> 00:01:18.140
Just be true to yourself until the end

24
00:01:18.270 --> 00:01:22.980
Set sail and grab it, DREAMIN ON

25
00:01:34.780 --> 00:01:39.620
<b>The Sake I Brewed to Drink With You</b>

26
00:01:45.090 --> 00:01:47.420
The island is flying?!

27
00:01:48.370 --> 00:01:52.720
Can this... truly be happening?!

28
00:01:53.220 --> 00:01:57.170
Just how powerful is Kaido?!

29
00:01:58.220 --> 00:01:59.730
What?!

30
00:01:59.730 --> 00:02:01.100
Why?!

31
00:02:01.100 --> 00:02:03.190
How come?!

32
00:02:04.690 --> 00:02:06.480
Marco the Phoenix?!

33
00:02:06.480 --> 00:02:08.940
<b>Marco the Phoenix

Former Whitebeard Pirate</b>

34
00:02:08.940 --> 00:02:12.750
Well then, let's try this!

35
00:02:14.840 --> 00:02:16.530
Ouch! Ow, ow, ow!

36
00:02:16.530 --> 00:02:17.950
Chopper!

37
00:02:17.970 --> 00:02:21.040
Hot! Hot! I'm burning!

38
00:02:21.040 --> 00:02:23.870
Hey! That's going too far!

39
00:02:23.870 --> 00:02:26.710
I thought we were on the same side!

40
00:02:26.730 --> 00:02:27.880
Marco!

41
00:02:27.880 --> 00:02:29.750
Marco...!

42
00:02:33.340 --> 00:02:35.970
They sure are testy...

43
00:02:35.970 --> 00:02:38.330
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...

44
00:02:38.330 --> 00:02:40.640
Chopper! I'll put it out!

45
00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:43.810
It's burning my arm!

46
00:02:43.810 --> 00:02:45.690
It'll scorch me too–

47
00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:47.410
Or not?

48
00:02:47.410 --> 00:02:48.980
This flame...

49
00:02:48.980 --> 00:02:51.440
Ouch! Ouch! Ow, ow...

50
00:02:49.400 --> 00:02:51.440
Chopper, you can relax!

51
00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:52.150
Huh?

52
00:02:52.150 --> 00:02:53.850
It's really hot–

53
00:02:53.850 --> 00:02:55.110
Or not?

54
00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:58.200
I'm on fire but I'm not getting burned!

55
00:02:58.490 --> 00:03:02.020
This flame is comfortably...

56
00:03:02.020 --> 00:03:03.650
warm...

57
00:03:03.650 --> 00:03:05.670
– Dr. Chopper!
– Dr. Chopper!

58
00:03:05.670 --> 00:03:07.830
We're ready to produce the antibodies!

59
00:03:07.830 --> 00:03:09.380
Come quickly!

60
00:03:09.630 --> 00:03:12.050
<b>Miyagi, Mink Doctor</b>
<b>Tristan, Mink Nurse</b>

61
00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:15.880
It's a swarm of ice ogres!

62
00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:20.180
Miyagi! Tristan! Get out of here!

63
00:03:20.180 --> 00:03:22.390
Gotta warm them up one way or another!

64
00:03:25.270 --> 00:03:27.640
Phoenix Pyreapple!

65
00:03:32.650 --> 00:03:34.190
Yeow!

66
00:03:34.190 --> 00:03:36.450
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow, ow...

67
00:03:37.490 --> 00:03:40.740
Oh, it's not that hot...

68
00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:46.860
The chill in my body is fading!

69
00:03:47.460 --> 00:03:49.180
Ow, ow, ow, ow...

70
00:03:49.740 --> 00:03:51.120
What?!

71
00:03:51.120 --> 00:03:53.340
Wh-What was I...?!

72
00:03:53.340 --> 00:03:55.260
Omasa!

73
00:03:55.260 --> 00:03:58.170
Thank goodness! You came to your senses!

74
00:03:59.720 --> 00:04:01.600
Omasa...!

75
00:04:01.600 --> 00:04:05.270
Well, it's like you were saying.
It's sapping your body heat.

76
00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:09.940
Once your stamina runs out,
you'll turn back into an ogre!

77
00:04:09.940 --> 00:04:12.900
I only bought you a bit of time!

78
00:04:16.690 --> 00:04:17.900
You're a lifesaver!

79
00:04:18.530 --> 00:04:20.700
Time's just what the doctor ordered!

80
00:04:21.450 --> 00:04:23.280
Miyagi! Tristan!

81
00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:25.370
Are you two okay?!

82
00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:28.540
Y-Yes!

83
00:04:28.540 --> 00:04:30.170
We're fine!

84
00:04:30.170 --> 00:04:32.670
Let's hurry and get to work!

85
00:04:32.670 --> 00:04:35.510
We'll give you the support you need!

86
00:04:35.510 --> 00:04:39.840
Thank you! I can focus if I'm in that tower!

87
00:04:42.300 --> 00:04:44.060
Marco!

88
00:04:44.640 --> 00:04:49.270
He and that damn tanuki really
know how to chap my ass!

89
00:04:49.270 --> 00:04:53.900
Hey, you bums! Catch that tanuki already!

90
00:04:53.900 --> 00:04:57.190
Why would he bother
saving your lousy asses?!

91
00:04:57.190 --> 00:05:00.400
But... that tanuki...

92
00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:03.120
Keep your eyes on the prize!

93
00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:08.620
If you don't wanna bite the dust,
crush that tanuki and take back the antibody!

94
00:05:09.250 --> 00:05:14.130
I see... I think I've got the gist of the situation.

95
00:05:14.130 --> 00:05:16.090
Hey, Roronoa!

96
00:05:16.090 --> 00:05:19.420
Weren't you on your way
to slice 'n dice Kaido?

97
00:05:21.010 --> 00:05:22.800
If you wanna get to the rooftop...

98
00:05:23.550 --> 00:05:25.260
I'll give you a lift!

99
00:05:25.260 --> 00:05:28.810
You guys are too good to be
dealing with these chumps!

100
00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:34.060
But Chopper needs our support...!

101
00:05:37.690 --> 00:05:41.450
Don't worry... Sir Skeleton!

102
00:05:41.740 --> 00:05:45.320
We'll hold the line for Sir Tanuki!

103
00:05:49.410 --> 00:05:51.710
Thanks, you guys! I'm counting on you!

104
00:05:57.460 --> 00:06:00.970
Hold it, you son of a bitch!

105
00:06:02.840 --> 00:06:04.090
Apoo!

106
00:06:07.260 --> 00:06:09.890
Give me back the antibody...!

107
00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:15.270
If I lose it...

108
00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:19.110
my ass is freakin' grass!

109
00:06:19.730 --> 00:06:21.150
Give it a rest!

110
00:06:21.150 --> 00:06:23.240
He won't stay down!

111
00:06:23.240 --> 00:06:25.950
I don't mind taking on one more job!

112
00:06:27.830 --> 00:06:30.490
Sir Tanuki, hurry into the tower!

113
00:06:44.300 --> 00:06:47.850
– Apoo!
– Apoo!

114
00:06:46.890 --> 00:06:50.930
<b>X Drake
Formerly of the Soaring Six
Ancient Saur-Saur Fruit: Allosaurus</b>

115
00:06:50.930 --> 00:06:52.310
This guy...

116
00:06:52.310 --> 00:06:53.980
Drake?!

117
00:06:53.980 --> 00:06:56.230
So he really has switched sides!

118
00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:07.450
Roronoa Zoro. If you would
consider me an ally...

119
00:07:07.910 --> 00:07:10.080
then I'll hold them here while you go ahead!

120
00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:16.960
At least you know how
to bet on the winning horse!

121
00:07:18.210 --> 00:07:21.880
<b>4th Floor



Inside

the Castle</b>

122
00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:21.880
Sanji! Sanji!

123
00:07:22.380 --> 00:07:28.640
Perhaps Sanji sensed a powerful foe
and went to hold them back on the third floor!

124
00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:29.550
Maybe...!

125
00:07:30.010 --> 00:07:32.430
Guess my observation haki isn't that good yet.

126
00:07:32.890 --> 00:07:35.850
I'm not picking up Sanji's presence at all!

127
00:07:40.820 --> 00:07:43.280
Do you feel something, Jinbe?!

128
00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:44.530
Yeah...

129
00:07:45.070 --> 00:07:47.410
There are quite a few enemies in here...

130
00:07:47.410 --> 00:07:49.410
And...

131
00:07:49.410 --> 00:07:52.030
they're quite strong!

132
00:07:58.210 --> 00:08:02.170
Seems like one of us
should remain on this floor!

133
00:08:04.170 --> 00:08:07.260
I'll create an opening. You go on ahead!

134
00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:10.930
Let's do this!

135
00:08:11.050 --> 00:08:12.930
General...

136
00:08:12.930 --> 00:08:15.270
Launcher!

137
00:08:21.860 --> 00:08:26.570
<b>Right-Brain Tower

Inside the Dome</b>

138
00:08:26.570 --> 00:08:29.950
Time to raise a little hell!

139
00:08:29.950 --> 00:08:31.820
General...

140
00:08:31.820 --> 00:08:33.530
Cannon!

141
00:08:34.540 --> 00:08:36.830
Get back, men!

142
00:08:45.210 --> 00:08:48.260
Who the hell fires something so haphazardly?!

143
00:08:51.140 --> 00:08:54.010
You're asking for it!

144
00:08:55.680 --> 00:08:58.140
I dig the look, bro!

145
00:09:03.150 --> 00:09:04.730
A triceratops!

146
00:09:05.400 --> 00:09:09.240
<b>Sasaki
Soaring Six
Ancient Saur-Saur Fruit: Triceratops</b>

147
00:09:09.240 --> 00:09:10.860
So you're a dinosaur!

148
00:09:10.860 --> 00:09:15.160
Just give up! This is the strongest
creature that ever lived!

149
00:09:16.450 --> 00:09:19.580
You'll be nothing but scrap
when I'm done with you!

150
00:09:19.580 --> 00:09:23.880
There's no scratching the sheen of Wapometal!

151
00:09:38.850 --> 00:09:44.560
<b>Outside

the Onigashima

Dome</b>

152
00:09:42.190 --> 00:09:44.310
It's the Soaring Six!

153
00:09:44.810 --> 00:09:48.360
<b>Ulti
Soaring Six
Ancient Saur-Saur Fruit: Pachycephalosaurus</b>
<b>Page One
Soaring Six
Ancient Saur-Saur Fruit: Spinosaurus</b>

154
00:09:53.820 --> 00:09:56.450
Where did they go?!

155
00:09:56.780 --> 00:10:00.120
I am ever so vexed!

156
00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:04.920
I shall crack her detestable head
wide open! That bitch!

157
00:10:16.390 --> 00:10:18.510
He ran off that way!

158
00:10:17.050 --> 00:10:17.100
<b>Banquet Hall

3rd Floor

Inside the Castle</b>

159
00:10:17.100 --> 00:10:17.140
<b>Banquet Hall

3rd Floor

Inside the Castle</b>

160
00:10:17.140 --> 00:10:17.180
<b>Banquet Hall

3rd Floor

Inside the Castle</b>

161
00:10:17.180 --> 00:10:18.510
<b>Banquet Hall

3rd Floor

Inside the Castle</b>

162
00:10:18.510 --> 00:10:20.060
Slow down, silly!

163
00:10:20.060 --> 00:10:21.770
Wait for us!

164
00:10:26.110 --> 00:10:28.070
Damn! What is this?!

165
00:10:28.650 --> 00:10:30.110
Let me out!

166
00:10:30.110 --> 00:10:32.950
You can stop struggling now...

167
00:10:33.650 --> 00:10:37.240
Be a good boy... Don't try to run.

168
00:10:38.740 --> 00:10:40.330
After all...

169
00:10:40.740 --> 00:10:44.540
didn't you say that you loved me?

170
00:10:46.670 --> 00:10:46.710
<b>Black Maria
Soaring Six
Ancient Spider-Spider Fruit: Rosamygale Grauvogeli</b>

171
00:10:46.710 --> 00:10:46.750
<b>Black Maria
Soaring Six
Ancient Spider-Spider Fruit: Rosamygale Grauvogeli</b>

172
00:10:46.750 --> 00:10:46.790
<b>Black Maria
Soaring Six
Ancient Spider-Spider Fruit: Rosamygale Grauvogeli</b>

173
00:10:46.790 --> 00:10:46.830
<b>Black Maria
Soaring Six
Ancient Spider-Spider Fruit: Rosamygale Grauvogeli</b>

174
00:10:46.830 --> 00:10:46.880
<b>Black Maria
Soaring Six
Ancient Spider-Spider Fruit: Rosamygale Grauvogeli</b>

175
00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:49.670
<b>Black Maria
Soaring Six
Ancient Spider-Spider Fruit: Rosamygale Grauvogeli</b>

176
00:10:54.930 --> 00:10:59.180
Stay by my side forever. I'll make you my pet.

177
00:10:59.180 --> 00:11:01.970
Don't be ridiculous! I...

178
00:11:01.970 --> 00:11:03.680
I have somewhere to be!

179
00:11:04.020 --> 00:11:04.980
But...

180
00:11:07.650 --> 00:11:08.860
everywhere...

181
00:11:09.440 --> 00:11:11.230
I look...

182
00:11:11.230 --> 00:11:13.990
it's women, women, women...!

183
00:11:16.570 --> 00:11:18.070
Is this...

184
00:11:18.070 --> 00:11:19.490
heaven?

185
00:11:20.660 --> 00:11:22.750
He's clearly lost it.

186
00:11:24.040 --> 00:11:26.330
You're absolutely precious...

187
00:11:26.370 --> 00:11:29.460
<b>Big Cat Cafe

4th Floor</b>

188
00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:34.300
So Straw Hat went on ahead...

189
00:11:34.300 --> 00:11:37.800
This'll be a real headache for ol' Kaido...

190
00:11:41.060 --> 00:11:43.060
Would you kindly stop...

191
00:11:43.720 --> 00:11:45.850
picking on my men?

192
00:11:45.850 --> 00:11:45.890
<b>Who's-Who
Soaring Six
Ancient Cat-Cat Fruit: Saber-Toothed Tiger</b>

193
00:11:45.890 --> 00:11:45.940
<b>Who's-Who
Soaring Six
Ancient Cat-Cat Fruit: Saber-Toothed Tiger</b>

194
00:11:45.940 --> 00:11:45.980
<b>Who's-Who
Soaring Six
Ancient Cat-Cat Fruit: Saber-Toothed Tiger</b>

195
00:11:45.980 --> 00:11:46.020
<b>Who's-Who
Soaring Six
Ancient Cat-Cat Fruit: Saber-Toothed Tiger</b>

196
00:11:46.020 --> 00:11:46.060
<b>Who's-Who
